<p>
<b>Q: How do I chat with other players?</b>
<br>
<b>A</b>: Press the return key to activate the chat window before typing your message.  
Press it again when done typing to send your text to other players.
</p>

<b>Q: How do I exit?</b>
<br><b>A:</b> Press the F12 key. 

